{
  "stem": "25651.12",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all that happened was they had some petrol bombs that they somehow smuggled into the compound.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they filled the building with natural gas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what exploded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's the-- you know, the natural gas was used for burning bodies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So people talk about all kinds of bomb-making and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's just imagination.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, that's the last I saw of Galen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- What happened to him?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He escaped?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in 20 minutes, these 300 men were all gunned down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, the other Sonderkommando men had to burn them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And now, the situation was that with these dire punishments, which the Germans always meted out to people who were not really responsible, you know, they took-- they took hostage.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They sort of had a method of a hostage punishment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were thinking of all-- we were thinking all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But instead, the Germans started dismantling the crematoria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And the rumors about the Russians became stronger and stronger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I prepared myself clothes without prisoner markings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, because if any time was to escape, now was the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in December when they said that Auschwitz would be evacuated and whoever wants to leave on the first march can leave, I, in fact, volunteered for the first march.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had a blanket, which I organized.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I was equipped, more or less, you know, to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had good clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had the skiing boots that Galen gave me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where were you marching to?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, the Germans wouldn't--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, just evacuated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were being evacuated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the point was to get out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
